                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7621" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0233</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2680 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">备战IPO：S公司经营现金流内控进阶之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Preparing for IPO: The Road to Advanced Internal Control of Operating Cash Flow of Company S</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李万福，张鹏飞，姜珊，张玉函</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金埔园林股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">首次公开募股；经营现金流；内部控制</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Initial public offering; Operating cash flow; Internal control</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">健全内部控制是企业备战IPO时的重要必修课，内部控制不健全将直接影响IPO进程。经营现金流是企业生存的前提和持续发展的保障，其内部控制健全与否是IPO审核的重点之一。本案例以园林绿化行业的领头羊S公司备战IPO时的经营现金流内控进阶之路为主线，复现了“S公司综合考虑园林绿化行业资金垫付频繁、工程回款滞后、经营现金流紧张的行业特点，以及上市后股民盈利要求增加、公司业务规模扩大、应收及应付账款进一步增加的可能性，选择未雨绸缪，实现采购与付款、销售与收款、研发与生产等多个环节经营现金流入与流出的内控进阶，最终成功上市”的心路历程。本案例旨在引导学员思考备战IPO的企业可如何优化经营现金流相关内部控制，助力企业成功上市并行稳致远。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Unsound internal control will negatively impact the IPO process, making it a crucial requirement for businesses preparing for an IPO. Operating cash flow is a requirement for an enterprise’s survival and sustained growth, and whether or not its internal controls are effective is one of the main focuses of an IPO audit. This case focuses on the internal control progression of the operating cash flow of S. Company, a market leader in landscaping. As S. Company prepared for its initial public offering (IPO), it decided to plan and hire a consulting team after taking into account the industry’s frequent capital advances, lagging project returns, and tight operating cash flow, as well as the possibility of increased shareholder profitability requirements, expansion of the company’s scale, and further growth in accounts receivable after listing, and chose to prepare and realize the progression of the internal control of the operating cash inflow and outflow in many aspects such as purchasing and payment, sales collection, and research and development, etc., and finally successfully listed. This case aims to guide participants to think about how enterprises preparing for IPO can optimize internal controls related to operating cash flow to help them successfully go public and make steady progress.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制的意义；经营现金流管理的重要性；“采购与付款业务、销售与收款业务、研究与开发业务”内部控制缺陷及其整改措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
